6. Why don‚Äôt we visit the city by bus or taxi? Coimbra is a medieval city and, in its historical center, most streets are only pedestrian and it‚Äôs not allowed for cars to drive there. In these small alleys it will be possible to discover hidden ‚Äúsecrets‚Äù and ‚Äútreasures‚Äù and no-way-out streets that only with our help you can figure out! We‚Äôre going to walk slowly and appreciate the landscape and our culture in between the downtown and uptown Coimbra. Our city has more charm walking! If you have mobility issues you can ask us ‚Äì in advance ‚Äì to adapt the visit in order to include transportation so we can combine both worlds (walking + transportation)!

